What would you like added/supported?

Support super.post_randomize()

```
package uvm_pkg;
class uvm_sequence_item;
endclass
endpackage
package tb_cpu_pkg;
   import uvm_pkg::*;
     class tb_cpu_seq_item extends uvm_sequence_item;
    function void post_randomize();
       super.post_randomize();
    endfunction
endclass : tb_cpu_seq_item
endpackage : tb_cpu_pkg;
module tb_cpu;
endmodule
```

```
verilator --cc --timing -Wno-fatal --top-module tb_cpu test.sv
%Error: test.sv:9:14: Can't find definition of task/function: 'post_randomize'
    9 |        super.post_randomize();
      |              ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~
```

**VCS compiles w/o any problem**

What 'verilator --version' are you using?  Did you try it with the git master version?

